  "title": "Production Supervisor (Tuas, $4.5k)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:<br />\n• Supervise steel bar bending operations and monitor shopfloor progress.<br />\n• Ensure works follow drawings, schedules and quality standards.<br />\n• Manage manpower, materials and equipment efficiently.<br />\n• Resolve production and safety issues.<br />\n• Maintain compliance with safety and quality requirements.<br />\n<br />\nRequirements:<br />\n• Diploma in Engineering or related field<br />\n• Relevant production supervision experience (steel fabrication preferred)<br />\n• Strong leadership and problem-solving skills<br />\n• Able to work on rotating shifts if required<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Please submit your\nresume in MS Word format to </strong><a href=\"mailto:sunnie@united-personnel.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>sunnie@united-personnel.com</strong></a></p><p>Please rememberto\ninclude your<br />\n1) Recent photo<br />\n2) Current salary & Expected salary<br />\n3) Notice period</p><p><strong>UNITED\nPERSONNEL SERVICES</strong><br />\n21 Bukit Batok Crescent<br />\n#02-75 WCEGA Tower<br />\nSingapore 658065<br />\nTel: +65 65651939<br />\nwww.united-personnel.com<br />\n<br />\nEA Licence Number: 05C5278<br />\nRegistration No.: R1103477<br />\n<br />\n(All applications will be treated in strictest confidence. We regret that only\nshortlisted candidates would be notified)</p>",
