    "description": "<p>Based in Singapore, <strong>UNITED PERSONNEL SERVICES</strong> belongs to a new breed of companies that are built on the foundation of a different philosophy, a new way of thinking.<br>\n<br>\nWe are a team of professionals who, through a clear understanding of businesses, and access to a network of quality professionals, are committed to creating a whole new concept in what is broadly known as the recruitment business.<br>\n<br>\nWe aim to make a difference to our clients by providing high quality advice on human resource management issues and by proactively supplying them with the best available people. How we go about doing it is that we keep our ears to the ground, get into the thick of the action and get our hands dirty. We make it a point to understand our client's business and industry just as much as themselves.<br>\n<br>\nWith our extensive contacts in the region, namely in countries such as Malaysia, Thailand, Myanmar, Philippines, Indonesia &amp; China, we give our clients an extra edge over competitors in terms of garnering timely and suitable talents especially in times of a tight labour market.<br>\n<br>\nWe specialise in the following areas:<br>\n• Oil &amp; Gas, Petrochemical &amp; Pharmaceutical Industries<br>\n• Engineering &amp; Construction Industries<br>\n• IT &amp; Technology Industries<br>\n• Semiconductor &amp; Hi-tech Manufacturing Industries<br>\n• Logistics and Supply Chain Management Industries<br>\n• Brand Management &amp; Graphic Packaging Industries<br>\n<br>\nContact us at:<br>\n21 Bukit Batok Crescent<br>\n#02-75 WCEGA Tower<br>\nSingapore 658065<br>\nOpen from Mondays - Fridays from 9.30am - 6.30pm<br>\nCall us at: (65) 6562 2321 / (65) 6565 1939</p>",
